Bye, Dad!

832
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:55,135
Bye, Dad.

833
00:44:00,306 --> 00:44:04,144
Exactly where is this train headed?

834
00:44:05,278 --> 00:44:06,179
All aboard!

835
00:44:06,179 --> 00:44:09,716
Oh! I want off. Now!

836
00:44:09,716 --> 00:44:13,319
You were intending on traveling, right?
Find your seats!

837
00:44:13,319 --> 00:44:14,187
Excuse me, ma’am.

838
00:44:14,187 --> 00:44:16,022
Get your hands off my book!
I mean my bag. Bozo.

839
00:44:16,222 --> 00:44:19,025
I’m sorry.
Everyone says I’m clumsy.

840
00:44:19,025 --> 00:44:19,959
Everyone’s right.

841
00:44:19,959 --> 00:44:22,462
Well, mostly it’s my dad.
He says that.

842
00:44:22,462 --> 00:44:26,299
Grow up, Bozo, and don’t complain
about family to me.

843
00:44:28,335 --> 00:44:30,770
And don’t be asking me for a ticket.

844
00:44:30,077 --> 00:44:32,546
Dragged off to who knows where.

845
00:44:33,239 --> 00:44:34,674
To magic! Wonder!

846
00:44:34,674 --> 00:44:36,142
All sorts of discoveries!

847
00:44:36,142 --> 00:44:38,011
Realizations that open the heart.

848
00:44:38,378 --> 00:44:39,813
Tickets, please!

849
