without Your guide

856
00:45:58,091 --> 00:46:02,262
Wouldn’t You accept me the way I am?

857
00:46:02,262 --> 00:46:08,335
Your hard tests are difficult to pass!

858
00:46:09,836 --> 00:46:13,573
I value You alone and no one else!

859
00:46:15,075 --> 00:46:18,142
This You must have known since long ago.

860
00:46:19,446 --> 00:46:24,484
O Master of heaven and earth,

861
00:46:24,484 --> 00:46:27,887
Lord of infinite Love,

862
00:46:27,887 --> 00:46:33,026
High above all sorrows and pleasures

863
00:46:33,026 --> 00:46:38,932
You own my very heart!

864
00:46:44,871 --> 00:46:49,509
Wouldn’t You accept him the way he is?

865
00:46:49,509 --> 00:46:52,645
Your hard tests are difficult to pass!

866
00:46:54,481 --> 00:46:58,885
Wouldn’t You accept her the way she is?

867
00:46:59,352 --> 00:47:02,889
Your hard tests are difficult to pass!

868
00:47:03,823 --> 00:47:08,661
If You’re not there to hold our hands

869
00:47:08,661 --> 00:47:13,700
We’d fail immediately!

870
00:47:13,007 --> 00:47:17,645
Wouldn’t You accept us the way we are?

871
00:47:18,338 --> 00:47:22,442
Your hard tests are difficult to pass!

872
00:47:23,109 --> 00:47:26,312
Accept me just the way…

873
00:47:26,946 --> 00:47:31,384
Accept me just the way…

874
00:47:32,485 --> 00:47:46,032
Accept me just the way I am!

875
00:48:26,039 --> 00:48:28,174
Nobody accepts me the way I am.

876
00:48:28,174 --> 00:48:30,076
What just happened here?
(Nobody.)

877
00:48:30,076 --> 00:48:32,345
Did anybody else see
what happened here?

878
00:48:32,345 --> 00:48:33,580
We went through Paris!

879
00:48:33,058 --> 00:48:35,627
I told you! Lots of things to see.

880
00:48:36,149 --> 00:48:38,685
It was Paris! Paris, people!

881
00:48:38,685 --> 00:48:42,889
Fabulous scenery!
But there’s more to experience!

882
00:48:42,889 --> 00:48:44,657
Would you like a baguette?

883
00:48:47,016 --> 00:48:49,118
A glass of “nectar”?

884
00:48:49,262 --> 00:48:50,530
Huh?

885
00:48:50,053 --> 00:48:51,388
Would you like some juice?

886
00:48:54,834 --> 00:48:56,336
It’s happening again!

887
00:48:56,336 --> 00:48:58,304
Are you hearing this?
Or is it just me?

888
00:48:58,738 --> 00:49:01,574
Or maybe it’s something I had for breakfast.

889
00:49:19,192 --> 00:49:25,665
While I am athirst in the desert of existence,

890
00:49:25,665 --> 00:49:29,936
You’re drinking Nectar
somewhere in the heavenly abode!

891
00:49:30,097 --> 00:49:32,366
If only I knew the road,

892
00:49:33,239 --> 00:49:37,677
I’d go up there and snatch it immediately.

893
00:49:38,211 --> 00:49:40,280
O Master,

894
00:49:40,028 --> 00:49:42,997
Gloriest of all Glory!

895
00:49:44,017 --> 00:49:46,553
Wouldn’t You consider it fair

896
00:49:46,553 --> 00:49:50,657
To spill down just a few drops

897
00:49:50,657 --> 00:49:51,858
Just a few drops

898
00:49:51,858 --> 00:49:53,493
For me?

899
00:49:58,998 --> 00:50:00,500
If only I know where You hide

900
00:50:00,005 --> 00:50:02,107
I’d come running to seek.

901
00:50:05,538 --> 00:50:07,173
But alas! As I’m born blind

902
00:50:07,173 --> 00:50:10,577
Couldn’t climb the highest peak.

903
00:50:10,577 --> 00:50:12,912
Even worse, being deaf and dumb

904
00:50:12,912 --> 00:50:17,250
I can never call, nor hear Your voice.

905
00:50:17,951 --> 00:50:19,552
O Jah (Lord),

906
00:50:19,986 --> 00:50:23,690
You’ve created this poor soul

907
00:50:23,069 --> 00:50:25,538
Everyone would tell me this.

908
00:50:26,159 --> 00:50:27,494
So please take care of it.

909
00:50:27,494 --> 00:50:30,163
Or it’ll die alone miserably.

910
00:50:30,463 --> 00:50:31,297
You know it

911
00:50:31,297 --> 00:50:32,632
Too well!

912
00:50:34,601 --> 00:50:36,136
You have eyes

913
00:50:36,136 --> 00:50:37,871
Come to fetch me.

914
00:50:37,871 --> 00:50:38,972
You have a mouth

915
00:50:38,972 --> 00:50:41,274
Please give me a call.

916
00:50:41,274 --> 00:50:43,176
You have ears

917
