00:51:01,494 --> 00:51:03,830
Master,

925
00:51:03,083 --> 00:51:05,786
I’d like to make a deal with You:

926
00:51:06,533 --> 00:51:09,602
We exchange roles for a few minutes.

927
00:51:10,097 --> 00:51:14,001
Then You may discover a deep secret –

928
00:51:14,874 --> 00:51:19,512
Or may just remember:

929
00:51:19,512 --> 00:51:22,215
How painful to be separated

930
00:51:22,215 --> 00:51:23,683
From Your very Self!

